{"abstract":[{"text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSURL"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"url"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The URL to process.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"url"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"return-value","level":2,"text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YES if the URL was handled by Pushwoosh, NO otherwise."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handles special Pushwoosh URLs, primarily used for:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Test device registration","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Register device for push testing via QR code","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Deep link tracking","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Process tracked deep links from push notifications","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Should be called from your app’s URL handling methods. Returns YES if the URL","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"was a Pushwoosh URL and was handled, NO if it should be processed by your app."}]},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle URLs in SceneDelegate (iOS 13+):"}]},{"code":["class SceneDelegate: UIResponder, UIWindowSceneDelegate {","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, openURLContexts URLContexts: Set<UIOpenURLContext>) {","        guard let url = URLContexts.first?.url else { return }","","        \/\/ First, check if Pushwoosh handles this URL","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            Logger.info(\"URL handled by Pushwoosh\")","            return","        }","","        \/\/ Handle other deep links","        DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, continue userActivity: NSUserActivity) {","        guard userActivity.activityType == NSUserActivityTypeBrowsingWeb,","              let url = userActivity.webpageURL else { return }","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return","        }","","        UniversalLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}","","\/\/ Legacy AppDelegate support","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ app: UIApplication,","                    open url: URL,","                    options: [UIApplication.OpenURLOptionsKey: Any] = [:]) -> Bool {","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return true","        }","","        return DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"title":"handleOpenURL:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handleOpenURL:"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handleOpenURL:":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality."}],"title":"handleOpenURL:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[]}}}